Stefan,

Great advice about this idea, i just did a 2 minute session using 
your settings and i think i got some good stuff.  I will post a file 
i just got next.  I think when you are in tune to get communication 
with the other side, it doesn&#39;t matter whether it&#39;s a box or Evp 
Maker.  If they want to talk with you, you will get communication 
with whatever you use.  I&#39;ve had success with manual sweeps as well, 
boxes are just easier to use for most of us.

-Steve H.



